definitions.definition: ( slang , vulgar , chiefly in the plural ) A person's breast or nipple .
( slang , vulgar ) An animal's teat or udder .
( UK , Ireland , derogatory , slang ) An idiot ; a fool .
examples: Look at that tit driving on the wrong side of the road!

definitions.definition: ( UK , Ireland , slang , derogatory ) A police officer ; a " tithead ".

definitions.definition: A chickadee ; a small passerine bird of the genus Parus or the family Paridae , common in the Northern Hemisphere.
Any of various other small passerine birds.
A young girl , later especially a minx , hussy .
